    "created_at": "2015-12-29T04:03:17Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-29T04:03:17Z",
    "body": "Disabling webview when node integration is off could have compatibility issues with existing apps, I think we can provide an option to disable webview. I have create #3943 for this.\n"
  },
